ProtoDefines:
. "A sequence $\{u_n\}$ in a metric space $(A,\rho)$ converges
   to $u\in A$ if $ \lim_{n\to\infty}\rho(u_n,u)=0. $ In this 
   case we say that $\lim_{n\to\infty}u_n=u$."
